spec.description: Comprehensive dashboard for Grafana Faro - web vitals, errors, performance, logs, and user sessions

spec.expr: sum(count_over_time({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | kind="measurement" | page_url!="" [$__auto]))
quantile_over_time(0.50, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | type="web-vitals" | presentation_delay!="" | unwrap presentation_delay [$__auto]) by (page_url)
quantile_over_time(0.75, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | type="web-vitals" | presentation_delay!="" | unwrap presentation_delay [$__auto]) by (page_url)
quantile_over_time(0.95, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | type="web-vitals" | presentation_delay!="" | unwrap presentation_delay [$__auto]) by (page_url)
sum by(type) (rate({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | kind="exception" | type!="" [$__auto]))
sum by(page_url) (rate({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | kind="exception" [$__auto]))
{service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | kind="exception"
sum by(page_url) (rate({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | kind="measurement" | page_url!="" [$__auto]))
sum by(browser_name) (rate({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | kind="measurement" | browser_name!="" [$__auto]))
quantile_over_time(0.50, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | type="web-vitals" | next_paint_time!="" | unwrap next_paint_time [$__auto]) by (page_url)
quantile_over_time(0.95, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | type="web-vitals" | next_paint_time!="" | unwrap next_paint_time [$__auto]) by (page_url)
quantile_over_time(0.50, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | type="web-vitals" | interaction_time!="" | unwrap interaction_time [$__auto]) by (page_url)
quantile_over_time(0.95, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | type="web-vitals" | interaction_time!="" | unwrap interaction_time [$__auto]) by (page_url)
sum by(context_rating) (rate({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | type="web-vitals" | context_rating!="" [$__auto]))
sum by(context_load_state) (rate({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | type="web-vitals" | context_load_state!="" [$__auto]))
sum(rate({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | kind="exception" [$__auto]))
sum by(session_id) (rate({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | kind="measurement" | context_interaction_type="pointer" [$__auto]))
sum by(browser_name, browser_version) (rate({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | kind="measurement" | browser_name!="" [$__auto]))
sum by(level) (rate({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt [$__auto]))
topk(10, sum by(page_url) (count_over_time({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | kind="measurement" | page_url!="" [$__auto])))
count(count by(session_id) (count_over_time({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | session_id!="" [$__auto])))
avg(avg_over_time({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | type="web-vitals" | interaction_time!="" | unwrap interaction_time [$__auto]))
quantile_over_time(0.95, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | type="web-vitals" | inp!="" | unwrap inp [$__auto]) by (service_name, deploment_environment)
quantile_over_time(0.50, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | type="web-vitals" | inp!="" | unwrap inp [$__auto]) by (page_url)
quantile_over_time(0.75, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | type="web-vitals" | inp!="" | unwrap inp [$__auto]) by (page_url)

quantile_over_time(0.50, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | type="web-vitals" | input_delay!="" | unwrap input_delay [$__auto]) by (page_url)
quantile_over_time(0.75, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | type="web-vitals" | input_delay!="" | unwrap input_delay [$__auto]) by (page_url)
quantile_over_time(0.95, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | logfmt | type="web-vitals" | input_delay!="" | unwrap input_delay [$__auto]) by (page_url)
